  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the ball in first person and try not to get motion sick! A movement system that is so relentless, unexpected and fun will put your gaming skills to the ultimate test! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/33fd6d02cf377df900ae963c246af46d.avif?t=1742551267\" width=616 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/afd99df48c163121068028b4046acc01.poster.avif?t=1742551267\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/afd99df48c163121068028b4046acc01.webm?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/afd99df48c163121068028b4046acc01.mp4?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each location is made in a unique style and provides unique gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/4058c726efc7461a4b48bb72e1ddf059.avif?t=1742551267\" width=616 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/cbad85d650d2744141c21eb8799eb116.poster.avif?t=1742551267\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/cbad85d650d2744141c21eb8799eb116.webm?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/cbad85d650d2744141c21eb8799eb116.mp4?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend hours trying and failing the same path! I promise someone will find it funny how you scream at the computer screen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/f1a8cf8483015ffe0d0844fe36529d7e.avif?t=1742551267\" width=616 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/d950ee4b4299396a0fb3555d121776e9.poster.avif?t=1742551267\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/d950ee4b4299396a0fb3555d121776e9.webm?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/d950ee4b4299396a0fb3555d121776e9.mp4?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your ball </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dizzying gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of rage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three difficulties: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy - Third person only</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medium - First person while moving, third person while idle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard - First person only<br>    </p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to get angry, laugh and cry as you race for the ball in an adventure that is challenging to play but impossible to put down. <br><br>Are you ready for the challenge? </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the ball in first person and try not to get motion sick! A movement system that is so relentless, unexpected and fun will put your gaming skills to the ultimate test! <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/33fd6d02cf377df900ae963c246af46d.avif?t=1742551267\" width=616 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/afd99df48c163121068028b4046acc01.poster.avif?t=1742551267\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/afd99df48c163121068028b4046acc01.webm?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/afd99df48c163121068028b4046acc01.mp4?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each location is made in a unique style and provides unique gameplay.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/4058c726efc7461a4b48bb72e1ddf059.avif?t=1742551267\" width=616 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/cbad85d650d2744141c21eb8799eb116.poster.avif?t=1742551267\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/cbad85d650d2744141c21eb8799eb116.webm?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/cbad85d650d2744141c21eb8799eb116.mp4?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend hours trying and failing the same path! I promise someone will find it funny how you scream at the computer screen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/f1a8cf8483015ffe0d0844fe36529d7e.avif?t=1742551267\" width=616 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/d950ee4b4299396a0fb3555d121776e9.poster.avif?t=1742551267\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/d950ee4b4299396a0fb3555d121776e9.webm?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3550920/extras/d950ee4b4299396a0fb3555d121776e9.mp4?t=1742551267\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your ball </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dizzying gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A lot of rage</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three difficulties: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy - Third person only</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Medium - First person while moving, third person while idle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hard - First person only<br>    </p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to get angry, laugh and cry as you race for the ball in an adventure that is challenging to play but impossible to put down. <br><br>Are you ready for the challenge? </p>",
